    {
      "type": "text", "id": "secrets_table_t",
      "x": 96, "y": 702, "width": 940, "height": 200,
      "text": "HCLOUD_TOKEN        hetzner cloud api  -  used only by terraform; never reaches the box.\nINVITE_SECRET       HMAC key  -  signs /r/<slug>?invite=... links + server verifies them.\nLIVEKIT_API_KEY     identifies the agent + token-minter to LiveKit server.\nLIVEKIT_API_SECRET  signs LK JWTs minted by /api/token; matches livekit.yaml keys.\nDEEPGRAM_API_KEY    STT streaming auth (used by agent only).\nGOOGLE_API_KEY      misc google api auth (env var).\nGCP_SA_JSON         google cloud TTS service account JSON (file at /etc/voicehook/gcp-sa.json).",
      "originalText": "HCLOUD_TOKEN        hetzner cloud api  -  used only by terraform; never reaches the box.\nINVITE_SECRET       HMAC key  -  signs /r/<slug>?invite=... links + server verifies them.\nLIVEKIT_API_KEY     identifies the agent + token-minter to LiveKit server.\nLIVEKIT_API_SECRET  signs LK JWTs minted by /api/token; matches livekit.yaml keys.\nDEEPGRAM_API_KEY    STT streaming auth (used by agent only).\nGOOGLE_API_KEY      misc google api auth (env var).\nGCP_SA_JSON         google cloud TTS service account JSON (file at /etc/voicehook/gcp-sa.json).",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
